87}]}, {\"sentence\": \"As I watched the exhilarating 1,500-meter race unfold, it became clear that the triumphs of Hocker and Nuguse were not merely about personal victories but about embodying the very essence of the American spirit.\", \"from\": 4290, \"to\": 4501, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4485, \"end\": 4493, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.999972629881397, \"rank\": 2.2949146921314575e-05, \"text\": \"American\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the exhilarating 1,500-meter race unfold\", \"from\": 4303, \"to\": 4343}, {\"ngram\": \"the triumphs\", \"from\": 4366, \"to\": 4378}, {\"ngram\": \"Hocker\", \"from\": 4382, \"to\": 4388}, {\"ngram\": \"Nuguse\", \"from\": 4393, \"to\": 4399}, {\"ngram\": \"personal victories\", \"from\": 4422, \"to\": 4440}, {\"ngram\": \"the very essence\", \"from\": 4461, \"to\": 4477}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Their performances were a testament to qualities that often feel overshadowed in today's climate: perseverance, unity, and a quiet but resolute determination.\", \"from\": 4502, \"to\": 4660, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Their performances\", \"from\": 4502, \"to\": 4520}, {\"ngram\": \"a testament\", \"from\": 4526, \"to\": 4537}, {\"ngram\": \"qualities\", \"from\": 4541, \"to\": 4550}, {\"ngram\": \"today's climate\", \"from\": 4583, \"to\": 4598}, {\"ngram\": \"perseverance\", \"from\": 4600, \"to\": 4612}, {\"ngram\": \"unity\", \"from\": 4614, \"to\": 4619}, {\"ngram\": \"a quiet but resolute determination\", \"from\": 4625, \"to\": 4659}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Their success demonstrates that greatness does not always manifest in loud or brash displays but in letting actions speak for themselves and rising to the moment.\", \"from\": 4661, \"to\": 4823, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Their success\", \"fr